alert dns any any -> any any (msg:"[Salamander CTI] Data Insufficient infrastructure domain"; dns.query; content:"s3.ru-3.storage.selcloud.ru"; nocase; classtype:trojan-activity; reference:url,https://salacti.com; sid:6100001; rev:1;)
alert dns any any -> any any (msg:"[Salamander CTI] Data Insufficient infrastructure domain"; dns.query; content:"bots.pepesoft.ru"; nocase; classtype:trojan-activity; reference:url,https://salacti.com; sid:6100002; rev:1;)
alert dns any any -> any any (msg:"[Salamander CTI] Data Insufficient infrastructure domain"; dns.query; content:"grandrp.su"; nocase; classtype:trojan-activity; reference:url,https://salacti.com; sid:6100003; rev:1;)
